00:10:26.570 --> 00:10:31.140
It’s what you do with chips, or fried chicken, or the fish in “fish and chips”.

00:10:32.160 --> 00:10:36.690
And a deep fried Mars bar is exactly what you probably think it is.

00:10:37.210 --> 00:10:43.710
The Mars bar is chilled, put in a fridge, before being covered in batter and then deep fried.

00:10:45.340 --> 00:10:49.070
If you like fried food and you like Mars bars, it will

